s meijer pronounced meyer is a retail giant in the midwest the companys huge combination grocery and general merchandise stores average  to  sq ft each or about the size of four regular grocery stores and stock about  items including meijer privatelabel products meijer operates more than  locations half are in michigan while the rest spread across four other nearby states customers can choose from plus departments including apparel electronics hardware and toys most stores also sell gasoline offer banking services and have multiple instore restaurants founder hendrik meijer opened his first store in  the business is still family owned and run key executives and contact counts for meijer inc identify and reach decision makers who have been verified by multiple contact methods executives phoneemail hendrik g meijer cochairman and coceo premium access locked content we have executives phone numbers and email addresses on file this is optional data available to you when building lead lists and with professional subscriptions doug meijer cochairman premium access locked content we have executives phone numbers and email addresses on file this is optional data available to you when building lead lists and with professional subscriptions mark a murray coceo and vice chairman premium access locked content we have executives phone numbers and email addresses on file this is optional data available to you when building lead lists and with professional subscriptions  other executives on file company contacts  of contacts marketing t we have contacts available for this company you may purchase these contacts from our lead lists sales t we have contacts available for this company you may purchase these contacts from our lead lists technology t we have contacts available for this company you may purchase these contacts from our lead lists top industries for meijer inc need to reach more people no problem research more than  million people for titles biographies and more access mo